long description: The unique diversiform silhouette of our Ascencio Candle Holder lifts light onto the shoulders of eight staggered openwork metal towers; while its hinged design allows for the concentration or extension of soft candlelight. Rustic metalwork offers the look of textured industrial sheeting, completing the design.
brand bio: Dimond Home is an award-winning designer and premier provider of lighting, accent furnishings, original art, and decorative accessories emphasizing fashionable trends, inviting color palettes, and uncommon organics. www.dimond-home.com. A division of ELK Group International
